               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān maḥyäwi “The Life-Giving Homily” (fols. 2ra-85va)&#xD;
I-1) Introductory prayer (fol. 2ra-rb)&#xD;
I-2) Reading for Monday, Compline (nǝwam) (fols. 2va-14ra)&#xD;
I-3) Reading for Tuesday, Matins (manfaqa lelit) (fols.14ra-27va)&#xD;
I-4) Reading for Wednesday, Lauds (nagh) (fols. 27va-37va)&#xD;
I-5) Reading for Thursday, Terce (śalastu säʿat) (fols. 37va-52ra)&#xD;
I-6) Reading for Friday, Sext (qätr) (fols. 52ra-63ra)&#xD;
I-7) Reading for Saturday, None (täsaʿtu säʿat) (fols. 63ra-74rb)&#xD;
I-8) Reading for Sunday, Vespers (śark) (fols. 74rb-85va)&#xD;
II) Malkǝʾa madḫane ʿālam “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 85va-91ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
